d%20that%20the%20former%20Principal%20was%20given%20the%20same%20role%20in%20another%20college%20hours%20after%20he%20resigned%20and%20said%20he%20must%20be%20immediately%20relieved%20of%20duties%20and%20sent%20on%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ghosh%20stepped%20down%20yesterday%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20cannot%20take%20the%20humiliation%20on%20social%20media%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20doctor's%20rape-murder.%20Hours%20later%2C%20he%20was%20given%20a%20new%20role%20as%20the%20Principal%20of%20Calcutta%20National%20Medical%20College.%20This%20sparked%20a%20wave%20of%20protest%2C%20as%20protesting%20doctors%20questioned%20the%20rush%20behind%20his%20new%20appointment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPulling%20up%20the%20state%20government%20for%20giving%20a%20new%20role%20to%20Dr%20Ghosh%20shortly%20after%20his%20resignation%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20appropriate%20authority%20should%20have%20borne%20in%20mind%20the%20circumstances%20under%20which%20the%20resignation%20was%20given.%20Therefore%2C%20even%20that%20resignation%20was%20not%20accepted%2C%20the%20least%20that%20can%20be%20expected%20from%20the%20department%20is%20to%20release%20the%20Principal%20from%20the%20administrative%20responsibility%20and%20not%20assign%20him%20any%20other%20duty%20of%20equal%20responsibility.%20This%20professor%20has%20been%20made%20Principal%20of%20another%20medical%20college.%20It%20is%20not%20clear%20as%20to%20what%20was%20the%20urgency%20in%20doing%20so.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20that%20Dr%20Ghosh%20is%20the%20first%20person%20whose%20statement%20must%20have%20been%20recorded%20by%20investigators.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20doubt%20his%20professional%20skills%20but%20once%20he%20is%20appointed%20principal%20he%20is%20a%20an%20administrator.%20You%20should%20have%20recorded%20his%20statement%2C%20why%20protect%20him%3F%20There%20is%20something%20amiss.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hospital%20administration%2C%20the%20court%20noted%2C%20was%20not%20with%20the%20victim%20or%20the%20family%20of%20the%20victim.%20%26quot%3BThe%20case%20on%20hand%20is%20a%20peculiar%20case.%20There%20should%20be%20no%20further%20loss%20of%20time.%20There%20may%20be%20possibility%20of%20evidence%20being%20tampered%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20also%20noted%20that%20it%20would%20have%20given%20more%20time%20to%20state%20police%20under%20%26quot%3Bnormal%20circumstances%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BEven%20after%20five%20days%20there%20have%20been%20no%20significant%20conclusions%20which%20should%20have%20happened%20by%20now.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20are%20justified%20that%20there%20is%20every%20possibility%20that%20evidence%20will%20be%20destroyed.%20We%20deem%20it%20appropriate%20that%20the%20case%20must%20be%20transferred%20to%20CBI%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20had%20said%20Kolkata%20Police%20must%20complete%20their%20probe%20by%20Sunday%2C%20failing%20which%20the%20state%20government%20would%20recommend%20a%20CBI%20probe%20if%20the%20victims'%20parents%20want.%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20had%20demanded%20a%20central%20agency%20probe%2C%20warning%20against%20tampering%20of%20proof%20if%20state%20police%20investigated%20the%20case%20that%20has%20sent%20shockwaves%20through%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723548540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fj35rjoq_kolkata-doctors_625x300_12_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctors-rape-murder-probe-to-be-transferred-to-cbi-high-court-6327984%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20nationwide%20protests%20over%20the%20chilling%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20doctor%20in%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20today%20ordere