%20received%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwini%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20last%20year%20I%20haven't%20been%20supported%20and%20it's%20ok.%20But%20you%20can't%20say%20I've%20been%20given%20Rs%201.5%20crore%2C%20if%20it's%20over%20four%20years%2C%20fair%20enough.%20As%20I%20was%20TOPS%20when%20I%20was%20partnering%20Sikki.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlaying%20her%20third%20Olympics%2C%20Ashwini%20was%20left%20in%20tears%20after%20she%20and%20her%20partner%20Tanisha%20couldn't%20win%20a%20single%20match%20to%20make%20an%20unceremonious%20exit%20from%20the%20group%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20haven't%20played%20well%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20coach%20not%20being%20there%2C%20I%20take%20responsibility%20for%20that.%20But%20you%20can't%20say%20I'm%20getting%20this%20amount%20when%20I%20haven't%20even%20got%20this%20amount%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723548180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F09rsqt0g_ashwini-ponnappa-and-tanisha-crasto_625x300_29_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fbadminton%2Ftelling-nation-that-i-got-money-is-ridiculous-ashwini-ponnappas-explosive-take-on-sports-authority-of-india-6328413%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20doubles%20badminton%20specialist%20Ashwini%20Ponnappa%20said%20she%20received%20little%20to%20no%20individual%20financial%20assistance%20from%20the%20sports%20ministry%20in%20the%20build%20up%20to%20Paris%20Olympics%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22EyeROV%20raises%20Rs%2010%20cr%20in%20pre-Series%20A%20round%20led%20by%20Unicorn%20India%20Ventures%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723