%3A%22Tarot%3A%20Where%20and%20how%20to%20watch%20the%20film%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723545258000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112494642%2Cimgsize-68858.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fenglish%2Ftarot-where-and-how-to-watch-the-supernatural-horror-film%2Farticleshow%2F112494622.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112494622.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20supernatural%20horror%20film%20%E2%80%98Tarot%E2%80%99%20made%20its%20debut%20on%20Netflix%20on%20August%203%2C%202024.%20Directed%20by%20Spenser%20Cohen%20and%20Anna%20Halberg%2C%20and%20based%20on%20Nicholas%20Adams'%201992%20novel%20%E2%80%98Horrorscope%2C%E2%80%99%20the%20film%20follows%20college%20students%20who%20unleash%20a%20sinister%20force%20by%20using%20an%20eerie%20deck%20of%20Tarot%20cards.%20The%20movie%20was%20also%20available%20for%20rent%20on%20Prime%20Video%20and%20ZEE5.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fenglish%2Ftarot-where-and-how-to-watch-the-supernatural-horror-film%2Farticleshow%2F112494622.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Water%2020%20km%20Below%20Mars%20Surface%3F%20What%20Study%20Shows%20And%20What%20It%20Means%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20study%20released%20Monday%20using%20data%20from%20NASA's%20Mars%20InSight%20lander%20shows%20evidence%20of%20liquid%20water%20far%20below%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20fourth%20planet%2C%20advancing%20the%20search%20for%20life%20there%20and%20showing%20what%20might%20have%20happened%20to%20Mars'%20ancient%20oceans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lander%2C%20which%20has%20been%20on%20the%20Red%20Planet%20since%202018%2C%20measured%20seismic%20data%20over%20four%20years%2C%20examining%20how%20quakes%20shook%20the%20ground%20and%20determining%20what%20materials%20or%20substances%20were%20beneath%20the%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20that%20data%2C%20the%20researchers%20found%20liquid%20water%20was%20most%20likely%20present%20deep%20beneath%20the%20lander.%20Water%20is%20considered%20essential%20for%20life%2C%20and%20geological%20studies%20show%20the%20planet's%20surface%20had%20lakes%2C%20rivers%20and%20oceans%20more%20than%203%20billion%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20Earth%20what%20we%20know%20is%20where%20it%20is%20wet%20enough%20and%20there%20are%20enough%20sources%20of%20energy%2C%20there%20is%20microbial%20life%20very%20deep%20in%20Earth's%20subsurface%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20of%20the%20authors%2C%20Vashan%20Wright%20of%20the%20University%20of%20California%20San%20Diego's%20Scripps%20Institution%20of%20Oceanography.%20%26quot%3BThe%20ingredients%20for%20life%20as%20we%20know%20it%20exist%20in%20the%20Martian%20subsurface%20if%20these%20interpretations%20are%20correct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20found%20that%20large%20reservoirs%20of%20liquid%20water%20in%20fractures%2011.5%20kilometres%20(7.15%20miles)%20to%2020km%20beneath%20the%20surface%20best%20explained%20the%20InSight%20measurements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20notes%20that%20the%20volume%20of%20liquid%20water%20predicted%20beneath%20the%20surface%20is%20%26quot%3Bmore%20than%20the%20water%20volumes%20proposed%20to%20have%20filled%20hypothesised%20ancient%20Martian%20oceans%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20Earth%2C%20groundwater%20infiltrated%20from%20the%20surface%26quot%3B%20to%20deep%20underground%2C%20Wright%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20this%20process%20to%20have%20occurred%20on%20Mars%20as%20well%20when%20the%20upper%20crust%20was%20warmer%20than%20it%20is%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20way%20to%20directly%20study%20water%20that%20deep%20beneath%20the%20surface%20of%20Mars%2C%20but%20the%20authors%20said%20the%20results%20%26quot%3Bhave%20implications%20for%20understanding%20Mars'%20water%20cycle%2C%20determining%20the%20fates%20of%20past%20surface%20water%2C%20searching%20for%20past%20or%20extant%20life%2C%20and%20assessing%20in%20situ%20resource%20utilization%20for%20future%20missions%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%2C%20whose%20other%20authors%20are%20Matthias%20Morzfeld%20of%20the%20Scripps%20Institution%20of%20Oceanography%20and%20Michael%20Manga%20of%20the%20University%20of%20California%20Berkeley%2C%20was%20published%20the%20week%20of%20Aug.%2012%20in%20the%20journal%20Proceedings%20of%20the%20National%20Academy%20of%20Sciences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20inspired%20and%20I%20hope%20the%20public%20is%20also%20inspired%2C%26quot%3B%20Wright%20said.%20%26quot%3BHumans%20can%20work%20together%20to%20put%20instruments%20on%20a%20planet...%20and%20try%20to%20understand%20what's%20going%20on%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723545000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fh34a0a8_mars_625x300_13_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmars-harbours-oceans-of-life-giving-water-deep-beneath-surface-study-6327101%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Water%20is%20considered%20essential%20for%20life%2C%20and%20geological%20studies%20show%20the%20planet's%20surface%20had%20lakes%2C%20rivers%20and%20oceans%20more%20than%203%20billion%20years%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmars-harbours-oceans-of-life-giving-water-deep-beneath-surface-study-6327101%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shraddha%2