%20L%C3%98CI%2C%20which%20also%20counts%20Nicki%20Minaj%20as%20an%20equity%20stakeholder.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Emmanuel%20Eribo%2C%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20L%C3%98CI%2C%20who%20worked%20in%20finance%20before%20becoming%20an%20entrepreneur.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20really%20considered%20a%20job%20in%20finance%20until%20I%20went%20out%20for%20drinks%20one%20day%20with%20a%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20ordering%20a%20lot%20of%20expensive%20drinks%2C%20wearing%20a%20nice%20suit%20and%20shoes%20and%20said%20%26quot%3BDon't%20worry%2C%20I'm%20a%20banker.%26quot%3B%20That%20was%20a%20lightbulb%20moment%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20have%20a%20financial%20background%20as%20I%20studied%20psychology%20at%20university.%20Still%2C%20I%20tried%20unsuccessfully%20to%20get%20into%20banking%20for%20about%20eight%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20while%20living%20rent-free%20at%20my%20mom's%20house%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20buy%20some%20books%20on%20coding%20and%20teach%20myself%20how%20to%20code.%20I%20was%20lucky%20enough%20to%20get%20a%20coding%20job%20at%20HSBC%20and%20started%20programming%20for%20the%20trading%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20a%20few%20months%2C%20I%20didn't%20feel%20like%20it%20was%20a%20culture%20fit%20and%20thought%20I%20would%20move%20on%20soon.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20my%20own%20boss%20and%20be%20in%20control%2C%20but%20because%20of%20the%20remuneration%20and%20lifestyle%20that%20comes%20with%20it%20I%20stayed%20in%20the%20finance%20industry%20for%20about%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20get%20involved%20in%20building%20something%20I%20could%20be%20responsible%20for%20%E2%80%94%20at%20that%20time%2C%20it%20was%20a%20venture%20into%20consumer%20products.%20My%20brother%2C%20and%20school%20friends%2C%20and%20I%20bounced%20ideas%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20telling%20my%20mom%20I%20was%20thinking%20of%20launching%20a%20business.%20She%20told%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20believe%20you%20can%20do%20it%2C%20I'm%20here%20for%20you.%26quot%3B%20That%20was%20all%20I%20needed%20because%20I%20started%20with%20nothing%2C%20and%20if%20I%20leave%20with%20nothing%2C%20I'll%20probably%20be%20OK%20in%20the%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20was%20very%20afraid%20to%20quit%20my%20job%2C%20but%20being%20an%20entrepreneur%2C%20that%20fear%20is%20constant%2C%20and%20you%20get%20comfortable%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20ended%20up%20building%20a%20business%20called%20Butterfly%20Twists%20as%20a%20side%20hustle.%20It%20was%20a%20ballerina%20shoe%20brand%20we%20built%20up%20as%20a%20hobby%20while%20we%20had%20finance%20jobs%20and%20distributed%20online.%20We%20started%20selling%20a%20lot%20of%20shoes%2C%20so%20we%20quit%20our%20jobs%20and%20built%20this%20brand%20up.%20It%20grew%20to%20have%20an%20office%20with%2060%20employees%20in%20the%20UK%20and%2030%20internationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Butterfly%20Twists%20shoes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bb2a1b955b01c3294df821%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShoes%20from%20Harley%20Viera-Newton's%20Butterfly%20Twists%20range.%3Cp%3EDave%20Benett%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20seven%20years%2C%20we%20learned%20how%20things%20worked%20in%20the%20industry.%20My%20time%20in%20banking%20taught%20me%20hard%20work%2C%20which%20was%20translated%20into%20running%20a%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EButterfly%20Twists%20grew%20significantly%3B%20we%20were%20selling%20in%2067%20countries%2C%20had%2032%20stores%2C%20and%20sold%20a%20million%20pairs%20of%20shoes%20a%20year.%20On%20the%20surface%2C%20we%20were%20doing%20amazing%2C%20but%20I%20wasn't%20in%20love%20with%20the%20business%20because%20I%20couldn't%20really%20relate%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20very%20proud%20of%20what%20we%20had%20achieved%2C%20but%20It%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20creating%20spreadsheets%20or%20PowerPoint%20presentations%20my%20entire%20time.%20The%20days%20of%20running%20around%20with%20sneakers%20in%20the%20bag%20and%20doing%20deals%20were%20long%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228904c379-42c8-4235-8bd0-57b6d6d9d27b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuilding%20a%20new%20brand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I%20considered%20whether%20I%20wanted%20to%20spend%20the%20next%20few%20years%20of%20my%20life%20on%20this%20business%20or%20do%20something%20I%20loved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friend%2C%20brother%2C%20and%20I%20spoke%20and%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BImagine%20if%20we%20could%20build%20another%20business%20that%20represented%20everything%20we%20believe.%26quot%3B%20That's%20when%20we%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20for%20L%C3%98CI%2C%20a%20luxury%20vegan%20sneaker%20and%20apparel%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Models%20wearing%20L%C3%98CI%20sneakers%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bb2a975da406397bf5499e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EL%C3%98CI%20footwear%20is%20worn%20by%20a%20number%20of%20celebrities.%3Cp%3EL%C3%98CI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EL%C3%98CI%20comes%20from%20the%20Latin%20word%20%26quot%3Blocus%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20means%20center%20or%20place%20and%20the%20feeling%20of%20being%20at%20home.%20We%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20business%20where%20we%20felt%20that%20way%20and%20built%20on%20our%20values%2C%20so%20we%20used%20repurposed%2C%20recycled%2C%20and%20biodegradable%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20our%20resources%20taking%20plastic%20out%20of%20the%20oceans%2C%20and%20from%20a%20human%20perspective%2C%20we've%20built%20a%20platform%20for%20artists%20and%20musicians.%20We%20host%20events%20at%20exclusive%20venues%20and%20hold%20performances%20with%20emerging%20artists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22663%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emmanuel%20Eribo%20and%20Charlotte%20Tilbury%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bb2e15b4912df3ae1b0a55%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22497%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEmmanuel%20Eribo%20with%20Charlotte%20Tilbury%20at%20Soho%20House%20in%20London.%3Cp%3EDavid%20M.%20Benett%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EL%C3%98CI%20is%20a%20platform%20for%20others%2C%20and%20for%20me%2C%20it%20allows%20me%20to%20be%20the%20person%20I%20want%20to%20be%2C%20express%20myself%2C%20and%20take%20control%20of%20my%20life.%20That's%20something%20I%20don't%20think%20working%20in%20finance%20offered%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20went%20to%20the%20US%20and%20started%20building%20relationships.%20When%20we%20launched%20L%C3%98CI%20in%202021%20we%20had%20no%20money%20but%20a%20dream%20of%20building%20a%20sneaker%20brand.%20It%20wasn't%20the%20skillset%20we%20had%2C%20but%20we%20knew%20how%20to%20build%20a%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20our%20launch%2C%20we've%20had%20a%20significant%20celebrity%20following%20who%20endorse%20our%20products%2C%20which%20was%20never%20something%20I%20could%20have%20dreamed%20of%20in%20the%20beginning.%20We've%20had%20Leonardo%20DiCaprio%20invest%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.lociwear.com%2Fstory%2F17345%2Fglobal-icon-nicki-minaj-becomes-an-owner-of-footwear-brand-l-ci%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENicki%20Minaj%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20equity%20stakeholder%2C%20too.%20We've%20also%20done%20an%20exclusive%20sneaker%20collaboration%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nicki%20Minaj%20posing%20whilst%20wearing%20a%20pair%20of%20pink%20sneakers%20from%20her%20collection%20with%20L%C3%98CI%5C%22%20char