esh-interim-govt-head-muhammad-yunus-on-temple-visit-calls-for-patience-amid-attacks-on-hindus%2Farticleshow%2F112493291.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Residents%20raised%20over%20%244%2C000%20to%20send%20their%20local%20street%20cleaner%20on%20vacation.%20His%20employer%20said%20he%20couldn't%20take%20the%20money.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222119%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Beach%20in%20Carvoeiro%2C%20Lagoa%2C%20Faro%20district%2C%20Algarve%2C%20Portugal.%20Photo%20shows%20a%20cliff%2C%20houses%2C%20sunbathers%20and%20swimmers%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bb2885b4912df3ae1b09af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELocals%20were%20fundraising%20to%20send%20Paul%20Spiers%20to%20Portugal.%3Cp%3EMarco%20Bottigelli%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EResidents%20of%20a%20London%20suburb%20raised%20%C2%A33%2C170%20(%244%2C050)%20to%20send%20their%20street%20cleaner%20on%20vacation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20his%20employer%20said%20that%20he%20couldn't%20accept%20the%20money%20under%20its%20gifting%20policies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELocals%20have%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20decision.%20One%20said%20that%20it%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20farcical%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20community%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20London%20raised%20%C2%A33%2C170%20(%244%2C050)%20to%20send%20its%20street%20cleaner%20on%20his%20second-ever%20overseas%20vacation%2C%20but%20his%20employer%20attracted%20ire%20when%20it%20said%20that%20he%20couldn't%20accept%20the%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Spiers%20has%20worked%20as%20a%20street%20cleaner%20in%20Beckenham%2C%20southeast%20London%2C%20since%202017%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fhelp-paul-go-to-portugal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoFundMe%20page%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Local%20