%20worried%20that%20he%20would%20lose%20his%20job%20if%20he%20accepted%20the%20money%20or%20the%20vacation%2C%20The%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20think%20he's%20still%20satisfied%20even%20if%20he%20doesn't%20get%20to%20go%2C%20but%20I%20feel%20like%20I've%20got%20his%20hopes%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Knight%2C%20who%20started%20the%20fundraiser%2C%20told%20the%20publication.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20just%20meant%20to%20be%20something%20nice%2C%20not%20something%20that's%20made%20a%20man%20who%20really%20needs%20the%20job%2C%20worried%20about%20the%20safety%20of%20his%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnight%20and%20other%20local%20residents%20hope%20that%20Veolia%20reverses%20its%20decision.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLiamConlonLabour%2Fposts%2Fpfbid0HWxm5WM1WJ2VgMACbsGaVv7KfdEEUYtqPJvZFp2yjuT7yyJgdPHcjd1jXQgYUFgPl%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELiam%20Conlon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20for%20Beckenham%20and%20Penge%2C%20said%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20disappointed%26quot%3B%20and%20asked%20the%20leader%20of%20Bromley%20Council%20what%20action%20it%20could%20take%20to%20ensure%20that%20Spiers%20could%20accept%20the%20gift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20absolutely%20farcical%20situation!%26quot%3B%20one%20person%20wrote%20on%20Facebook%20in%20response%20to%20a%20post%20by%20Conlon.%20Another%20person%20commented%20that%20they%20could%20understand%20why%20the%20policy%20existed%20in%20the%20case%20of%20conflicts%20of%20interest%2C%20but%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20ulterior%20motive%20here%20other%20than%20thanks%20from%20the%20general%20public.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocals%20have%20also%20posted%20in%20a%20community%20group%20on%20Facebook%20expressing%20their%20annoyance%20at%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnight%20wrote%20on%20the%20GoFundMe%20page%20that%20she%20would%20refund%20the%20donors%20if%20Veolia%20refused%20to%20change%20its%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERe