0over%20Delhi's%20jailed%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20decision%20to%20let%20minister%20Atishi%20hoist%20the%20national%20flag%20this%20Independence%20Day.%20The%20General%20Administration%20Department%20under%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20has%20termed%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20decision%20%26quot%3Binvalid%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20a%20decision%20on%20who%20will%20hoist%20the%20flag%20is%20awaited.%20The%20ruling%20AAP%20has%20described%20GAD's%20response%20as%20%26quot%3Bpetty%20politics%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20there%20should%20be%20no%20problem%20if%20an%20elected%20minister%20hoists%20the%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Environment%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20recently%20met%20Chief%20Minister%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20is%20in%20Tihar%20jail%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20corruption%20case%20linked%20to%20Delhi's%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy.%20Subsequently%2C%20Mr%20Rai%20asked%20GAD%20to%20make%20arrangements%20for%20the%20hoisting%20of%20the%20flag%20by%20Atishi%20Marlena%20in%20place%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GAD%2C%20however%2C%20said%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20cannot%20authorise%20Ms%20Atishi%20to%20hoist%20the%20national%20flag%20on%20his%20behalf.%20In%20response%20to%20Mr%20Rai's%20letter%2C%20GAD%20additional%20chief%20secretary%20Navin%20Kumar%20Chaudhary%20said%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20direction%20is%20%26quot%3Blegally%20invalid%20and%20cannot%20be%20acted%20upon%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20had%20also%20written%20to%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20is%20this%20connection%2C%20but%20his%20office%20said%20they%20did%20not%20receive%20any%20communication.%20Tihar%20jail%20authorities%20later%20told%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20that%20his%20letter%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Babuse%20of%20privileges%26quot%3B%20granted%20to%20him%20under%20the%20Delhi%20Prison%20Rules%20and%20was%20not%20not%20sent%20to%20Mr%20Saxena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGAD%20Cites%20%26quot%3BStature%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GAD%20has%20said%20that%20Independence%20Day%20and%20Republic%20Day%20are%20national%20events%20with%20supreme%20Constitutional%20sanctity%2C%20and%20any%20deviation%20or%20subjugation%20will%20not%20only%20undermine%20the%20sanctity%20associated%20with%20them%20but%20may%20also%20amount%20to%20statutory%20illegality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20detailed%20laid%20down%20provisions%20for%20celebrating%20them%20as%20per%20the%20stature%20they%20deserve%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20another%20other%20authority%20cannot%20fill%20in%20the%20place%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GAD%20said%20it%20is%20coordinating%20with%20all%20departments%20concerned%20for%20Independence%20Day%20celebrations%20at%20Chhatrasal%20stadium%20and%20the%20matter%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20absence%20has%20been%20raised%20with%20higher%20authorities.%20%26quot%3BThe%20issue%20has%20been%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20higher%20authorities%2C%20and%20a%20decision%20is%20awaited%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20an%20official%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManish%20Sisodia%20Slams%20'Flag%20Politics'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20AAP%20leader%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20who%20is%20out%20on%20bail%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case%2C%20has%20slammed%20there%20should%20be%20no%20problem%20with%20an%20elected%20minister%20hoisting%20the%20flag.%20%26quot%3BI%20read%20in%20the%20papers%20that%20when%20a%20conman%20Sukesh%20writes%20letter%2C%20the%20Tihar%20administration%20duly%20submits%20it%20to%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor's%20office.%20The%20LG%20too%20promptly%20takes%20action%20on%20it.%20But%2C%20when%20the%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20writes%20a%20letter%2C%20the%20LG%20asks%20Tihar%20officials%20not%20to%20send%20it%20to%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJailed%20conman%20Sukesh%20Chandrashekar%20has%20written%20several%20open%20letters%2C%20targeting%20AAP%20leaders%2C%20including%20Mr%20Kejriwal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lieutenant%20Governor's%20office%20should%20have%20asked%20the%20Tihar%20Jail%20director%20general's%20office%20to%20send%20Chief%20Minister%20Kejriwal's%20letter%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%2C%20they%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20independence%20or%20the%20country.%20People%20like%20Sukesh%20are%20beloved%20to%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtishi%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20is%20stopping%20Delhi's%20elected%20government%20from%20hoisting%20the%20government.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20can%20be%20a%20bigger%20dictatorship%20than%20this%3F%20We%20have%20to%20see%20if%20BJP%20is%20standing%20with%20democracy%20or%20dictatorship%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723542360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fuegdh5q8_sisodia-atishi_625x300_13_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fmanish-sisodia-arvind-kejriwal-aap-manish-sisodias-sukesh-parallel-to-slam-lt-governor-amid-flag-hoisting-row-6327880%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20massive%20row%20has%20erupted%20over%20Delhi's%20jailed%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20decision%20to%20let%20minister%20Atishi%20hoist%20the%20national%20flag%20this%20Independence%20Day.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fmanish-sisodia-arvind-kejriwal-aap-manish-sisodias-sukesh-parallel-to-slam-lt-governor-amid-flag-hoisting-row-6327880%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hindalco%20Q1%20result%3A%20PAT%20rises%2025.3%25%2C%20board%20appoints%20Ananya%2C%20Aryaman%20Birla%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723542294000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-07%2F19%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill