20to%20reduce%20it.%20Towards%20the%20end%2C%20sometimes%20we%20get%20desperate%20for%20even%20a%20sip%20of%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20just%20the%20night%20before%20the%20bout%2C%20we%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20sleep%20even%20two%20days%20before%2C%20since%20we%20have%20to%20remain%20empty%20stomach.%20When%20you%20don't%20eat%20anything%2C%20how%20would%20you%20sleep%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20an%20exemption%20should%20be%20given%20to%20wrestlers%20on%20the%20second%20day%20of%20their%20bout%2C%20Aman%20said%20that%20a%20limit%20of%202kg%20should%20be%20put%20in%20place%2C%20considering%20the%20brutality%20of%20the%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbout%202kg%20of%20exemption%20should%20be%20given%20for%20the%20weigh-in%20on%20the%20second%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bronze%20in%20Paris%20Olympics%20automatically%20makes%20Aman%20a%20contender%20for%20a%20medal%20at%20the%20LA%20Games%20in%202028.%20The%20wrestler%20is%20keen%20to%20return%20to%20training%20and%20prepare%20for%20the%20next%20Olympic%20Games.%20%26quot%3BI'll%20return%20and%20start%20practice%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20LA%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723538160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fltg4ghs8_aman-sehrawat-ndtv_625x300_13_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fmy-weight-increased-by-3-5kg-aman-sehrawat-narrates-weight-cut-brutality-to-ndtv-6327171%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20exclusive%20chat%20with%20NDTV%2C%20wrestler%20Aman%20Sehrawat%20revealed%20that%20his%20weight%20had%20increased%20by%203.5kg%20ahead%20of%20the%20second%20day%20of%20his%20events.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fmy-weight-increased-by-3-5kg-aman-sehrawat-narrates-weight-cut-brutality-to-ndtv-