E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heinous%20incident%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%2C%20where%20a%20female%20resident%20doctor%20was%20allegedly%20raped%20and%20murdered%20on%20the%20institute's%20premises%20on%20August%209%2C%20has%20sparked%20nationwide%20outrage%20among%20the%20medical%20community.%20Doctors%20from%20several%20hospitals%20across%20India%20have%20announced%20an%20indefinite%20strike%20to%20protest%20the%20gruesome%20crime.%20They%20have%20declared%20that%20all%20elective%20services%20(non-urgent%20and%20not%20medically%20necessary)%20will%20be%20suspended%20until%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20is%20completed.%20The%20strong%20reactions%20from%20resident%20doctors%20working%20in%20government%20colleges%20are%20understandable%20given%20the%20challenging%20conditions%20they%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20at%20government%20hospitals%2C%20often%20located%20on%20sprawling%20campuses%2C%20work%20in%20dark%20and%20poorly%20maintained%20areas.%20Security%20is%20lax%20in%20many%20sections%20of%20these%20hospitals%2C%20lacking%20technology%20or%20CCTV%20to%20monitor%20potential%20perpetrators.%20In%20contrast%2C%20private%20hospitals%20generally%20offer%20better%20security%20and%20working%20conditions%2C%20with%20improved%20access%20control%20and%20a%20safer%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENumerous%20cases%20have%20highlighted%20the%20vulnerability%20of%20women%20in%20the%20medical%20profession%20to%20sexual%20attacks%2C%20intimidation%2C%20and%20violence%20from%20patients%2C%20their%20attendants%2C%20hospital%20staff%2C%20colleagues%2C%20seniors%2C%20and%20teachers.%20Even%20female%20patients%20are%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kolkata%20incident%20evokes%20memories%20of%20the%20horrific%20assault%20on%20nurse%20Aruna%20Shanbaug%20at%20KEM%20Hospital%20in%20Mumbai%20in%201973.%20Aruna%20remained%20in%20a%20coma%20for%2042%20years%20before%20passing%20away%20in%202015.%20In%20May%202023%2C%20Dr%20Vandana%20Das%20was%20murdered%20by%20a%20drug%20addict%20brought%20to%20Kottarakkara%20Taluk%20Hospital%20in%20Kollam%2C%20Kerala.%20In%202019%2C%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20a%20mass%20resignation%20of%20doctors%20occurred%20after%20a%20mob%20attacked%20a%20junior%20doctor%2C%20triggered%20by%20the%20death%20of%20a%20patient%20and%20allegations%20of%20medical%20negligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20care%20for%20patients%2C%20work%20long%20hours%2C%20and%20sacrifice%20our%20personal%20time.%20Yet%2C%20when%20a%20patient%20dies%2C%20relatives%20often%20blame%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr%20Nikita%20Jain%2C%20a%20junior%20resident%20at%20a%20government%20medical%20college.%20%26quot%3BWho%20will%20safeguard%20our%20safety%2C%20our%20lives%2C%20and%20our%20well-being%3F%20It%20is%20shocking%20how%20we%20are%20treated%2C%20especially%20in%20light%20of%20recent%20incidents%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EA%20Tough%20Road%20For%20Students%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NMC%20data%20from%20February%202024%2C%20among%20those%20who%20dropped%20out%20of%20medical%20programmes%2C%20153%20were%20MBBS%20students%20and%201%2C117%20were%20in%20postgraduate%20courses.%20In%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20at%20least%20122%20medical%20students%2C%20including%20MBBS%20students%20and%20postgraduate%20doctors%2C%20died%20by%20suicide%20due%20to%20academic%20pressure%2C%20burnout%2C%20mental%20health%20challenges%2C%20hostile%20work%20environment%2C%20and%20punitive%20bond%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20students%20entering%20the%20medical%20profession%2C%20distress%2C%20mental%20stress%2C%20and%20uncertainty%20begin%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20fill%20out%20the%20NEET%20(National%20Eligibility%20cum%20Entrance%20Test)%20form.%20Many%20who%20qualify%20the%20NEET%20struggle%20with%20the%20vast%20medical%20syllabus%20and%20consider%20dropping%20out%20but%20are%20often%20compelled%20to%20continue%20due%20to%20financial%20constraints.%20Conditions%20for%20postgraduate%20residents%2C%20especially%20in%20larger%20medical%20colleges%2C%20are%20particularly%20dire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20states%20impose%20bond%20conditions%20on%20medical%20students%20at%20all%20levels-undergraduate%2C%20postgraduate%2C%20and%20super-specialty.%20There%20are%20two%20types%20of%20bonds%3A%20'seat%20leaving'%20bonds%20and%20'service'%20bonds.%20The%20former%20impose%20heavy%20fines%20on%20students%20who%20leave%20their%20courses%20prematurely%2C%20particularly%20postgraduate%20students%2C%20to%20deter%20resignations%20and%20avoid%20perceived%20waste%20of%20medical%20education.%20Service%20bonds%20require%20doctors%20to%20work%20in%20the%20state's%20healthcare%20system%20for%201-5%20years%20after%20completing%20their%20education%2C%20with%20penalties%20ranging%20from%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20to%20Rs%201%20crore%20for%20breaking%20the%20bond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NMC%20mandates%20a%20compulsory%20three-month%20residency%20posting%20at%20the%20district%20level%20for%20all%20postgraduate%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20Divesh%20Garg%2C%20a%2026-year-old%20resident%20doctor%20at%20a%20private%20medical%20college%20in%20Dehradun%2C%20died%20by%20suicide.%20His%20parents%20cited%20poor%20working%20conditions%20and%20harassment%20by%20seniors%20as%20factors%20leading%20to%20his%20death.%20Despite%20the%20pressure%2C%20he%20could%20not%20resign%20due%20to%20the%20prohibitive%20cost%20of%20the%20seat-leaving%20bond.%20In%20response%20to%20his%20death%2C%20the%20government%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20abolished%20the%20seat-leaving%20bond%20policy%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20state%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20challenges%2C%20young%20doctor%20interns%20often%20remain%20silent%20for%20fear%20of%20being%20bullied%2C%20victimised%2C%20or%20failing%20internal%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EImmediate%20Action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20Kolkata%20incident%2C%20the%20semi-naked%20body%20of%20the%20postgraduate%20doctor%20was%20found%20in%20a%20seminar%20room%2C%20underscoring%20the%20inadequate%20facilities%20for%20resident%20doctors%2C%20who%20lacked%20a%20designated%20rest%20area%20in%20a%20medical%20college%20in%20central%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20proper%20support%20staff%20for%20resident%20doctors%20to%20manage%20emergencies%20and%20other%20needs%20at%20night.%20Strict%20safety%20measures%2C%20such%20as%20cameras%20and%20security%20personnel%2C%20are%20essential%20in%20hospitals.%20Resting%20areas%20for%20resident%20doctors%20are%20basic%20necessities%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr%20Vasundhara%20Pawar%2C%20Vice%20President%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Medical%20Students'%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20of%20medical%20colleges%20needs%20to%20be%20regulated%20by%20the%20government%20and%20the%20NMC.%20The%20government%20must%20instruct%20the%20NMC%20to%20ensure%20safe%20and%20dignified%20working%20conditions%20for%20resident%20doctors.%20Mere%20assurances%20on%20paper%20are%20insufficient%20without%20concrete%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20moment%2C%20we%20expect%20the%20government%20and%20the%20NMC%20to%20investigate%20this%20case%20impartially%2C%20free%20from%20high-level%20influence%20or%20manipulation.%20A%20joint%20committee%20with%20resident%20doctors%20and%20NMC%20officials%20should%20be%20formed%20to%20address%20the%20issues%20faced%20by%20on-field%20doctors%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedical%20colleges%20must%20invest%20in%20suitable%20and%20safe%20lodging%20facilities%20for%20resident%20doctors.%20The%20long-overdue%20need%20for%20legislation%20to%20address%20violence%20against%20doctors%20and%20the%20abolition%20of%20punitive%20bonds%20must%20be%20urgently%20addressed.%20Disciplinary%20bodies%20at%20the%20college%2C%20state%2C%20and%20national%20levels%20should%20ensure%20that%20students%20can%20raise%20their%20concerns%20without%20fear%20of%20persecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20stipend%20scales%20vary%20across%20states%2C%20with%20many%20medical%20residents%20receiving%20inadequate%20compensation.%20It%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20medical%20colleges%20to%20provide%20well-structured%20education%20in%20a%20supportive%20environment%20without%20overburdening%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723537920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F7dv7j0ic_kolkata-doctor-protest_625x300_12_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fkolkata-rape-case-and-all-thats-wrong-with-indias-medical-system-6327330%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Kolkata%20incident%20evokes%20memories%20of%20the%20horrific%20assault%20on%20nurse%20Aruna%20Shanbaug%20at%20KEM%20Hospital%20in%20Mumbai%20in%201973.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fkolkata-rape-case-and-all-thats-wrong-with-indias-medical-system-6327330%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BExaggerated%20Narrative%26quot%3B%3A%20Mohandas%20Pai%20Rubbishes%20Hindenburg%20Charge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMohandas%20Pai%2C%20Economist%20and%20Aarin%20Capital%20Chairman%2C%20slammed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindenburg-report-fizzles-out-investors-trust-remains-in-stock-markets-6320926%5C%22%3EUS%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20publishing%20allegations%20against%20the%20SEBI%20chairman%20without%20any%20data.%20Mr%20Pai%20claimed%20Hindenburg's%20sole%20aim%20was%20to%20make%20money%20and%20there%20is%20no%20substance%20in%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20substance%20in%20the%20allegation.%20These%20guys%20are%20throwing%20mud%20at%20everybody%20for%20character%20assassination%20as%20they%20got%20a%20notice%20from%20SEBI%20because%20they%20have%20done%20insider%20trading%20in%20sort%20of%20a%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pai%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindenburg-has-no-credibility-at-all-mukul-rohatgi-on-fresh-allegations-6322370%5C%22%3Enew%20Hindenburg%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20claimed%20that%20SEBI%20Chairperson%20Madhabi%20Puri%20Buch%20and%20her%20husband%20Dhaval%20Buch%20had%20stakes%20in%20offshore%20entities%20involved%20in%20the%20alleged%20Adani%20money%20siphoning%20scandal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SEBI%20Chairman%20and%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20however%2C%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fadani-group-sebi-chief-madhavi-puri-buch-industry-leaders-slam-discredited-hindenburg-research-6314773%5C%22%3Elabelled%20these%20allegations%20as%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%26quot%3Bmalicious%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pai%20too%20claimed%20that%20there%20are%20several%20checks%20done%20by%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20while%20making%20appointments%20and%20there%20was%20no%20conflict%20of%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20are%20sensationalising%20saying%20there%20is%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest.%20How%20is%20there%20conflict%20of%20interest%20when%20there%20is%20no%20investment%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Infosys%20chief%20finance%20officer%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20investment%20was%20in%20a%20local%20fund%20in%20Singapore%20when%20they%20were%20residents%20there.%20The%20fund%20had%20no%20investments%20in%20Adani%20companies.%20Redeemed%20fully%20later.%20Perfectly%20legitimate%20legal%20vehicle%20in%20Singapore.%20The%20fund%20manager%20was%20regulated.%20No%20investment%20when%20she%20joined%20SEBI.%20So%20what%20is%20the%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20Hindenburg%20has%20no%20credibility%2C%20he%20urged%20investors%20and%20young%20people%20to%20not%20get%20carried%20away%20by%20fake%20narratives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhabi%20and%20Dhaval%20Buch%20have%20accused%20Hindenburg%20Research%20of%20attempting%20a%20character%20assassination%20of%20the%20SEBI%20chairperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHindenburg%20has%20been%20served%20a%20show%20cause%20notice%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20violations%20in%20India.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20instead%20of%20replying%20to%20the%20show%20cause%20notice%2C%20they%20have%20chosen%20to%20attack%20the%20credibility%20of%20SEBI%20and%20attempt%20character%20assassination%20of%20the%20SEBI%20Chairperson%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20couple%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20has%20also%20said%20Hindenburg%20Research%20has%20made%20%26quot%3Brecycled%20claims%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20discredited%20short-seller%20under%20the%20scanner%20for%20several%20violations%20of%20Indian%20securities%20laws%2C%20Hindenburg's%20allegations%20are%20no%20more%20than%20red%20herrings%20thrown%20by%20a%20desperate%20entity%20with%20total%20contempt%20for%20Indian%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20group%20said%20in%20an%20exchange%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723537740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F3qm7r3oc_mohandas-pai-ndtv_625x300_13_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fsensational-exaggerated-narrative-mohandas-pai-rubbishes-hindenburg-charge-6327263%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohandas%20Pai%2C%20Economist%20and%20Aarin%20Capital%20Chairman%2C%20slammed%20US%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%20for%20publishing%20allegations%20against%20the%20SEBI%20chairman%20without%20any%20data.%22%2C%22author%22%3A