%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20adequate%20geographic%20representation%20in%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20is%20responsible%20for%20its%20failures%2C%20and%20giving%20Africa%20permanent%20membership%20will%20be%20essential%20to%20make%20the%20highest%20decision-making%20body%20effective%2C%20R.%20Ravindra%2C%20charge%20d'affaires%20of%20India's%20UN%20mission%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20G-4%2C%20the%20group%20of%20India%2C%20Brazil%2C%20Germany%20and%20Japan%2C%20on%20Monday%20at%20an%20open%20debate%20of%20the%20Council%20on%20reforming%20itself%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20primary%20reason%20for%20the%20underperformance%20of%20this%20critical%20institution%20remains%20the%20non-representation%20of%20Africa%2C%20Latin%20America%20and%20the%20Caribbean%20and%20the%20under-representation%20of%20Asia-Pacific%20in%20the%20permanent%20category%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20convinced%20that%20African%20representation%20in%20both%20permanent%20and%20non-permanent%20categories%20will%20be%20an%20indispensable%20part%20of%20UNSC%20reform%20for%20a%20more%20representative%20and%20effective%20Council%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20of%20the%20Council%20was%20convened%20by%20Sierra%20Leone%2C%20which%20holds%20the%20rotating%20presidency%2C%20to%20push%20Africa's%20case%20for%20reforming%20the%20Council%20to%20give%20the%20continent%20better%20representation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESierra%20Leone's%20President%20Julius%20Maada%20Bio%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDespite%20being%20home%20to%20over%201.3%20billion%20people%2C%20and%20the%2054%20African%20countries%20making%20up%2028%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20membership%20of%20the%20UN%2C%26quot%3B%20Africa%20continues%20to%20suffer%20from%20the%20historic%20injustice%20of%20being%20deprived%20of%20permanent%20seats%20at%20the%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNearly%2080%20years%20after%20its%20creation%2C%20the%20Council%20has%20been%20stuck%20in%20time%26quot%3B%20--%201945%20when%20the%20UN%20was%20created%20while%20most%20of%20Africa%20was%20under%20the%20colonial%20yoke%20perpetuating%20the%20injustice%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfrica%20demands%20two%20permanent%20seats%20in%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20and%20two%20additional%20non-permanent%20seats%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20existing%20three%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ravindra%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20as%20G-4%20continue%20to%20support%20fully%20these%20legitimate%20demands%20and%20aspirations%20from%20the%20people%20of%20Africa%26quot%3B%20and%20its%20relationship%20with%20the%20continent%20%26quot%3B%20is%20anchored%20in%20trust%20and%20mutual%20respect%20and%20is%20focused%20on%20ensuring%20that%20Africa%20finds%20its%20rightful%20place%20in%20a%20new%20age%20of%20reformed%20multilateralism%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20also%20inconceivable%20that%20Africa%20which%20constitutes%20over%2070%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20UNSC's%20agenda%20items%20under%20discussions%2C%20does%20not%20get%20a%20permanent%20voice%20at%20the%20horse-shoe%20table%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20Council%20chamber%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ravindra%20said%20the%20Inter-governmental%20Negotiations%20(IGN)%20for%20Council%20reforms%20should%20expedite%20text-based%20negotiations%20so%20that%20it%20can%20proceed%20with%20the%20reform%20process%20in%20time%20for%20the%2080th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20UN%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20at%20the%20summit%20of%20G-20%20last%20year%20under%20India's%20leadership%2C%20Africa%20was%20given%20membership%20in%20the%20group%20of%20the%20major%20industrialised%20and%20emerging%20economies%2C%20which%20was%20also%20noted%20by%20Bio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBio%20said%20that%20Africa's%20claim%20should%20be%20treated%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20case%26quot%3B%20and%20given%20priority%20in%20reforming%20the%20Council%20in%20time%20for%20the%2080th%20anniversary%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20speakers%20at%20the%20meeting%20also%20emphasised%20Africa's%20case%20for%20special%20expedited%20treatment%20in%20the%20reform%20process%20mired%20for%20decades%20by%20opposition%20by%20a%20small%20group%20of%20countries%20that%20call%20themselves%20Uniting%20for%20Consensus%20(UfC)%20hoping%20to%20detach%20the%20continent%20from%20the%20controversies%20involving%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20its%20G4%20partners%20that%20work%20together%20to%20expand%20the%20Council%2C%20and%20other%20countries%20have%20counted%20on%20Africa's%20case%20for%20reform%20to%20break%20the%20stalemate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20calls%20for%20treating%20Africa%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20case%26quot%3B%20ahead%20of%20the%20Summit%20of%20the%20Future%20in%20September%20and%20the%20UN's%2080th%20anniversary%20next%20year%20seek%20to%20make%20the%20reform%20a%20piecemeal%20effort%20--%20if%20it%20happens%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarco%20Romiti%2C%20a%20Minister%20Counsellor%20in%20the%20UN%20Mission%20of%20Italy%20which%20heads%20the%20UfC%2C%20spoke%20out%20against%20adding%20more%20permanent%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMunir%20Akram%2C%20the%20permanent%20representative%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20which%20is%20also%20a%20member%20of%20UfC%2C%20opposed%20expanding%20permanent%20membership%20but%20said%20that%20Africa%20can%20be%20considered%20a%20special%20case%20and%20be%20given%20long-term%20seats%20in%20the%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%2C%20too%2C%20was%20firm%20against%20adding%20permanent%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBio%20was%20asked%20outside%20the%20Council%20chamber%20at%20his%20meeting%20with%20the%20media%20how%20he%20hoped%20to%20overcome%20the%20UfC%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Africa%20has%20a%20very%20compelling%20case%20and%20that%20is%20what%20we%20are%20pushing%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20consider%20the%20opposition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20genuine%20case%20and%20that%20is%20what%20we%20are%20pushing.%20We%20know%20that%20there%20are%20others%20%E2%80%A6%20it%20is%20a%20total%20reform%2C%20but%20we%20are%20talking%20for%20Africa%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20was%20confident%20that%20it%20was%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20Africa%20got%20its%20due.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20gatekeepers%20will%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20let%20us%20in%2C%20but%20as%20you%20can%20see%2C%20there%20is%20already%20willingness%20and%20as%20you%20can%20see%20we%20are%20gradually%20inching%20towards%20the%20next%20steps%20in%20order%20to%20be%20able%20to%20reach%20our%20goal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Akram%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20India%20and%20the%20G4%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BAfrica%20is%20critically%20different%20from%20the%20demand%20of%20four%20states%20for%20permanent%20membership%20for%20themselves%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20Permanent%20Representative%20Fu%20Cong%20also%20threw%20in%20criticism%20against%20India%20and%20the%20G4%2C%20saying%20that%20there%20were%20%26quot%3Ba%20few%20countries%20and%20interest%20groups%20who%20pursue%20their%20own%20selfish%20and%20small-circle%20interests%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Council%20reform%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20said%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bcracks%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Council's%20%26quot%3Bfoundation%20are%20becoming%20too%20large%20to%20ignore%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20contributing%20to%20deadlock%2C%20stalemate%20and%20stagnation%20around%20today's%20most%20pressing%20crises%20and%20they%20are%20feeding%20a%20broader%20crisis%20of%20credibility%20and%20legitimacy%20that%20is%20affecting%20multilateralism%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20accept%20that%20the%20world's%20preeminent%20peace%20and%20security%20body%20lacks%20a%20permanent%20voice%20for%20a%20continent%20of%20well%20over%20a%20billion%20people%20--%20a%20young%20and%20rapidly%20growing%20population%20--%20making%20up%2028%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20membership%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723535160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-08%2Fgg6u123_india-at-un-security-council-un-security-council-un-security-council-president_625x300_01_August_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-pakistan-try-to-derail-india-g4-nations-un-security-council-bid-6326239%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20lack%20of%20adequate%20geographic%20representation%20in%20the%20UNSC%20is%20responsible%20for%20its%20failures%2C%20and%20giving%20Africa%20permanent%20membership%20will%20be%20essential%20to%20make%20the%20top%20UN%20body%20effective%2C%20R.%20Ravindra%2C%20charge%20d'affaires%20of%20India's%20UN%20mission%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-pakistan-try-to-derail-india-g4-nations-un-security-council-bid-6326239%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ji.hlava%E2%80%99s%20Emerging%20Producers%20Reveal%20Pitches%20for%20Upcoming%20Projects%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723534859000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FEP-2024.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236104103%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ji.hlava%20Documentary%20Film%20Festival%20has%20revealed%20to%20Variety%20the%20projects%20that%20the%20participants%20of%20its%202024%20Emerging%20Producers%20program%20