ld%2Fuk%2Fuk-unemployment-wages-growth-drop-official-data%2Famp_articleshow%2F112488184.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fuk-unemployment-wages-growth-drop-official-data%2Famp_articleshow%2F112488184.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAccept%20Apology%2C%20However...%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%20Relief%20For%20Ramdev%2C%20And%20A%20Warning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYoga%20guru%20Ramdev%20and%20his%20aide%20Balakrishna%20today%20got%20some%20relief%20in%20a%20misleading%20ads%20case%20related%20to%20Patanjali%20products%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20closed%20contempt%20proceedings%20against%20them.%20The%20court%2C%20however%2C%20warned%20them%20against%20violating%20court%20orders%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Hima%20Kohli%20and%20Justice%20Sandeep%20Mehta%20said%20in%20their%20order%20that%20the%20court%20accepts%20the%20apology%20of%20Ramdev%20and%20Balakrishna.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20we%20expressly%20and%20strictly%20warn%20them%20that%20they%20will%20not%20do%20any%20thing%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20court%20orders%20like%20it%20has%20happened%20earlier%20in%20this%20case.%20We%20have%20come%20down%20heavily%20and%20we%20warn%20that%20this%20should%20not%20be%20done%20in%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20affidavits%20tendered%20before%20this%20court%20should%20be%20done%20with%20full%20truth.%20We%20close%20the%20contempt%20proceedings%20initiated%20against%20the%20party%20with%20the%20warning%20of%20adhering%20to%20the%20orders%20passed%20by%20this%20court%20in%20this%20case.%20The%20notice%20issued%20to%20present%20contemnor%20also%20stands%20discharge%20and%20closed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Yoga%20guru%20and%20his%20aide%20for%20misleading%20ads%20of%20Patanjali%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20dates%20back%20to%20the%20Covid%20years.%20Patanjali%20launched%20a%20drug%2C%20Coronil%2C%20in%202021%20and%20Ramdev%20described%20it%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20evidence-based%20medicine%20for%20COVID-19%26quot%3B.%20It%20also%20claimed%20that%20Coronil%20had%20certification%20from%20WHO.%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20disputed%20this%20claim%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bblatant%20lie%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20subsequent%20video%2C%20Ramdev%20was%20heard%20saying%20that%20allopathy%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bstupid%20and%20bankrupt%20science%26quot%3B.%20The%20IMA%20sent%20a%20legal%20notice%20to%20him%20and%20sought%20an%20apology.%20Patanjali%20Yogpeeth%20responded%20that%20Ramdev%20was%20reading%20out%20from%20a%20forwarded%20WhatsApp%20message%20and%20has%20no%20ill-will%20against%20modern%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20in%20August%202022%2C%20IMA%20moved%20a%20petition%20against%20Patanjali%20after%20it%20published%20an%20advertisement%20in%20newspapers%20titled%20'Misconceptions%20Spread%20By%20Allopathy%3A%20Save%20Yourself%20And%20The%20Country%20From%20The%20Misconceptions%20Spread%20By%20Pharma%20And%20Medical%20Industry'.%20The%20ad%20claimed%20that%20Patanjali%20drugs%20had%20cured%20people%20of%20diabetes%2C%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20thyroid%2C%20liver%20cirrhosis%2C%20arthritis%20and%20asthma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors'%20body%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bcontinuous%2C%20systematic%2C%20and%20unabated%20spread%20of%20misinformation%26quot%3B%20comes%20alongside%20Patanjali's%20efforts%20to%20make%20false%20claims%20about%20curing%20certain%20diseases%20through%20use%20of%20its%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2021%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20warned%20Patanjali%20against%20such%20claims%20and%20threatened%20to%20slap%20heavy%20fines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatanjali's%20counsel%2C%20court%20documents%20say%2C%20then%20assured%20that%20%26quot%3Bhenceforth%2C%20there%20shall%20not%20be%20any%20violation%20of%20any%20of%20the%20laws%2C%20especially%20relating%20to%20advertisement%20and%20branding%20of%20products%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2015%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20received%20an%20anonymous%20letter%20that%20mentioned%20misleading%20advertisements%20Patanjali%20continued%20to%20put%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20sought%20a%20reply%20from%20Patanjali%20on%20why%20contempt%20proceedings%20should%20not%20be%20initiated%20against%20it.%20On%20March%2019%2C%20the%20court%20was%20told%20that%20Patanjali%20had%20not%20filed%20the%20reply%20to%20the%20contempt%20notice.%20It%20then%20asked%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%20to%20appear%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%202%2C%20the%20court%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%20for%20their%20%26quot%3Babsolute%20defiance%26quot%3B%20over%20not%20filing%20proper%20affidavits%20over%20the%20misleading%20advertisements.%20The%20apologies%20that%20followed%20were%20rejected%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20they%20were%20sent%20to%20the%20media%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20firm%20put%20out%20an%20apology%20in%20newspapers%2C%20the%20court%20asked%20if%20the%20size%20of%20the%20apology%20was%20similar%20to%20its%20full-page%20advertisements%20of%20its%20products.%20Thereafter%2C%20Patanjali%20put%20out%20larger%20apologies%20in%20all%20prominent%20newspapers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723533240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F5v2rp03o_ramdev-ani-_625x300_10_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-closes-contempt-proceedings-against-ramdev-patanjali-6326751%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yoga%20guru%20Ramdev%20and%20his%20aide%20Balakrishna%20today%20got%20some%20relief%20in%20a%20misleading%20ads%20case%20related%20to%20Patanjali%20products%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20closed%20the%20contempt%20case%20against%20the