%20%E2%80%9CI%20felt%20it%20was%20important%20that%20people%20come%20and%20join%20this%20movement%20to%20make%20this%20initiative%20sustainable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20decade%20after%20its%20launch%2C%20the%20organisation%20began%20working%20on%20water%20conservation%20as%20well.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20sapling%20needs%20support%20for%20two%20to%20three%20years%2C%20including%20regular%20watering.%20However%2C%20we%20noticed%20that%20after%20planting%20saplings%20during%20the%20monsoon%2C%20it%20became%20challenging%20to%20find%20water%20to%20sustain%20them%20in%20the%20summer.%20While%20working%20on%20our%20plantation%20projects%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20water%20conservation%20also%20needs%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERejuvenating%20the%20once%20%E2%80%98City%20of%20Lakes%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20aptly%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98City%20of%20Lakes%E2%80%99%2C%20Bengaluru%20boasted%20a%20large%20number%20of%20lakes%20during%20the%20reign%20of%20the%20kings%20and%20the%20British.%20Satellite%20data%20collected%20by%20the%20Bangalore%20Metropolitan%20Region%20Development%20Authority%20(BMRDA)%20in%202001%20revealed%20that%20there%20were%202%2C789%20lakes%20in%20the%20city.%20Over%20time%2C%20many%20of%20these%20lake%20areas%20were%20transformed%20into%20residential%20and%20commercial%20entities%2C%20educational%20institutes%2C%20bus%20stands%2C%20stadiums%2C%20and%20dumping%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flh7-rt.googleusercontent.com%2Fdocsz%2FAD_4nXeccEy40hIKxFxKprPQQnK8Ne8IwphvqqnbZ0RvhrIknhPZnfU_rLDHUgtIOPKEdhDYIdOxlg6F_JBJu6JSzxS12PatbDpdXUtrNddvTvAaOkELl23Sarsp7KOvvtbtxhCwvbPA3GcACZsE25IoeD51fcQ%3Fkey%3Dbh9p4Y9Cbw8RlZeCoJr9pA%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20lakes%20are%20drying%20up%20owing%20to%20climate%20c