ow%20YouTube%20channels%20that%20organise%20editorial%20discussions.%20For%20instance%2C%20check%20out%20Harshit%20Dwivedi%20and%20Prashant%20Tiwari%20who%20provide%20current%20affair%20notes%20on%20Telegram%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-3-1723091250.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vikas%20advises%20aspirants%20to%20set%20weekly%20or%20monthly%20targets%20to%20remain%20consistent%20in%20studies.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-3-1723091250.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-3-1723091250-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-3-1723091250-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-3-1723091250-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-3-1723091250-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360262%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVikas%20advises%20aspirants%20to%20set%20weekly%20or%20monthly%20targets%20to%20remain%20consistent%20in%20studies.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20importance%20of%20keeping%20oneself%20updated%20about%20current%20affairs%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CYour%20first%20task%20of%20the%20day%20should%20be%20to%20study%20current%20affairs%20but%20aspirants%20neglect%20this%20section.%20They%20feel%20reading%20Vision%20365%20magazine%20at%20the%20last%20minute%20would%20be%20helpful.%20But%20you%20need%20to%20follow%20news%20articles%20daily%20and%20remain%20aware%20about%20daily%20happenings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Do%20not%20neglect%20qualifying%20paper%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECivil%20Services%20Aptitude%20Test%20or%20CSAT%20is%20GS%20Paper-2%20in%20the%20preliminary%20examination.%20It%20is%20conducted%20to%20evaluate%20an%20aspirant%E2%80%99s%20comprehension%2C%20logical%20reasoning%2C%20general%20mental%20ability%2C%20and%20basic%20numeracy%20skills.%20As%20it%20is%20a%20qualifying%20paper%20requiring%20a%20minimum%20of%2033%20percent%2C%20Vikas%20says%2C%20Hindi%20medium%20aspirants%20tend%20to%20neglect%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202023%2C%20the%20CSAT%20paper%20was%20very%20difficult.%20Most%20of%20the%20Hindi%20medium%20aspirants%20come%20from%20BA%20and%20BSc%20background%20and%20some%20lack%20reasoning%20and%20mathematics%20abilities.%20They%20lose%20their%20confidence%20in%20CSAT.%20Despite%20this%2C%20they%20focus%20on%20other%20subjects%20more.%20Remember%20to%20give%20equal%20weightage%20to%20such%20subjects%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%2C%20Vikas%20advises%20aspirants%20to%20set%20weekly%20or%20monthly%20targets%20to%20remain%20consistent%20in%20studies.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20not%20sleep%20if%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20complete%20my%20targets%20even%20if%20it%20was%203%20in%20the%20night.%20However%2C%20remember%20to%20take%20a%20day%E2%80%99s%20break%20sometimes%20to%20feel%20rejuvenated.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20it%20is%20just%20an%20exam.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723095244000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-2-1723091324.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D360088%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IFS%20officer%20Vikas%20Singh%20Meena%20shattered%20several%20stereotypes%20about%20Hindi%20medium%20aspirants%20by%20clearing%20the%20UPSC-CSE%202023%20examination%2C%20with%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%20672.%22%2C%22