g%20the%20monsoon.%20Gradually%2C%20he%20started%20selling%20fertilisers%20to%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20turning%20point%20came%20into%20his%20life%20in%202007%20when%20farmers%20were%20throwing%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurned%20adversity%20into%20opportunity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHrushikesh%20planted%204%2C000%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20between%20mango%20and%20%3Cem%3Eamla%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20gooseberry)%20trees.%20%E2%80%9CI%20thought%20there%20was%20no%20harm%20in%20growing%20aloe%20vera%20on%20my%20farm%2C%20even%20if%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20generate%20immediate%20income.%20I%20knew%20that%20aloe%20vera%20could%20work%20wonders%20as%20a%20termite%20repellent%20and%20would%20help%20protect%20my%20mango%20trees%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20graduate%2C%20who%20holds%20a%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20horticulture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20offline%20exhibitions%20organised%20in%20Satara%2C%20he%20often%20came%20across%20small%20entrepreneurs%20selling%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F237401%2Fman-earns-lakhs-aloe-vera-organic-online-fresh-products-self-help-groups-inspiring-rural-development-meghalaya-rongram-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealoe%20vera%20products%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CInspired%20by%20the%20idea%2C%20I%20started%20preparing%20products%20like%20soaps%2C%20shampoos%2C%20and%20aloe%20vera%20juice.%20But%20this%20did%20not%20bring%20me%20good%20profits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20his%20expertise%20in%20horticulture%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20utilise%20aloe%20vera%20to%20make%20natural%20pesticides%2C%20herbal%20spreader%2C%20and%20plant%20growth%20promoter.%20%E2%80%9CInsect%20thrips%20damage%20the%20buds%20and%20leaves%20of%20crops.%20I%20once%20mixed%20aloe%20vera%20with%20fish%20oil%20and%20sprayed%20it%20on%20crops.%20Pests%20and%20animals%20dislike%20it%20because%20of%20its%20bitter%20taste.%20I%20found%20this%20to%20be%20an%20effective%20pest%20repellent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hrushikesh%20utilises%20aloe%20vera%20to%20make%20natural%20pesticides%2C%20herbal%20spreader%2C%20and%20plant%20growth%20promoter.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360103%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHrushikesh%20uses%20aloe%20vera%20to%20make%20natural%20pesticides%2C%20herbal%20spreaders%2C%20and%20plant%20growth%20promoters.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CPlants%20like%20bananas%20naturally%20avert%20water%20on%20its%20surface.%20It%20becomes%20difficult%20for%20farmers%20to%20spray%20pesticides%20on%20their%20leaves.%20Spraying%20aloe%20vera%20spreader%20helps%20spread%20pesticide%20throughout%20the%20length%20of%20the%20plant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20Hrushikesh%20started%20commercialising%20these%20products%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20friends%20he%20made%20from%20marketing%20jobs.%20Today%2C%20he%20manufactures%20an%20ave