0if%20urban%20dwellers%20believe%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20living%20in%20an%20idyllic%20village%20in%20the%20mountains%20is%20charming%20and%20are%20likely%20to%20idealise%20it%2C%20the%20reality%20is%20far%20from%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20young%20Aprajita%20found%20city%20life%20alluring.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20I%20wanted%20to%20run%20away%20from%20this%20place%20as%20I%20felt%20there%20were%20no%20opportunities%20here.%20People%20didn%E2%80%99t%20respect%20farming%20then%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20live%20in%20a%20city%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20admits%20candidly%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETime%20is%20a%20funny%20thing%2C%20and%20adulthood%20makes%20us%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20the%20things%20we%20disliked%20as%20children.%20This%20third%20generation%20farmer%2C%20too%2C%20would%20find%20a%20deep%20set%20passion%20in%20farming%2C%20and%20ultimately%20make%20a%20career%20out%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20prevent%20middlemen%20from%20ripping%20off%20their%20earnings%2C%20Aprajita%20started%20selling%20their%20farm%20fresh%20apples%20directly%20online%20in%202021.%20In%20just%20two%20hours%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20sell%20300%20kg%2C%20ensuring%20that%20her%20parents%20received%20the%20right%20value%20for%20their%20hard%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20robust%20Instagram%20community%20helped%20as%20they%20immediately%20jumped%20on%20to%20the%20opportunity%20to%20have%20fresh%20apples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20soon%20registered%20her%20brand%20name%20%E2%80%98Phal%20Phool%E2%80%99%20through%20which%20she%20sells%20apples%2C%20flower%2C%20pulses%20%26amp%3B%20vegetable%20seeds%20directly%20to%20customers.%20The%20engineer%20quit%20her%20job%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20ago%20to%20pursue%20farming%20full%20time%2C%20with%20dreams%20of%20practising%20permaculture%20and%20creating%20a%20food%20forest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-