chieved%20at%20Karrylicious%20Kitchen%20is%20because%20of%20our%20roots%20and%20authenticity%20without%20which%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been%20possible.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParsi%20food%20has%20enjoyed%20an%20itinerant%20history.%20Farida%20underlines%20how%20every%20Parsi%20home%20has%20its%20own%20repository%20of%20culinary%20secrets.%20She%20gestures%20towards%20%3Cem%3Edhansak.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20and%20every%20home%20has%20its%20own%20recipe%20for%20this%20dish.%20And%20the%20taste%20also%20differs%20across%20households%2C%20but%20the%20taste%20quotient%20will%20be%20amazing%20irrespective%20of%20which%20home%20you%20eat%20it%20in.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20being%20said%2C%20taste%20profiles%20also%20change%20across%20generations.%20Farida%20agrees.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%20cooking%20I%20used%20to%20stay%20exactly%20true%20to%20my%20great-grandmother%E2%80%99s%20and%20mother%E2%80%99s%20recipes.%20But%20now%20I%20allow%20myself%20a%20little%20variation%2C%20a%20little%20additions%20here%20and%20there%20and%20a%20change%20in%20technique.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20example%20is%20the%20strawberry%20jam%20and%20custard%20cake%20in%20which%20Farida%20has%20deviated%20slightly%20from%20the%20original%20recipe%20and%20added%20a%20substitute%20for%20the%20usual%20milk.%20Another%20example%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3Esalli%20%3C%2Fem%3Echicken%20where%20she%20has%20added%20a%20few%20more%20ingredients%20and%20changed%20the%20technique%20of%20cooking%20the%20onions%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Emasala%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffood-3-1722423057.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pomfret%20curry%20(L)%20and%20veg%20cheese%20bakedish%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.the